# Organizations & SCPs

## The fleet as a tree

**Root** → nestable **OUs** → **accounts** (leaves).

- **Management account** — owns the org, pays bills, attaches SCPs. **No workloads here.**
- **Member** — every other account

## Why Organizations

Consolidated **billing** · programmatic **account creation** · centralized **governance** · **sharing** via RAM

## SCP — the governance lever

On root / OU / account → the **max permissions** in scope, **incl. member root**.

- **Does not grant** — only caps (IAM must still allow)
- **Skips** the management account + service-linked roles
- Deny-list (`FullAWSAccess` + `Deny`s) · patterns: **region restriction**, **`Deny` LeaveOrganization**
